task.summary: Created basic structure for NodeJS application
Restructured routes to allow modularisation, add auth router
Added auth utility with signup functionality
Refactored dbconnection utility to allow custom db config and insertions
Added copying of .json files in assets
Added error codes to be exposed to the client
Added login route and refactored for use of resolveErrorOnRoute()
Added login() function to return a jwt
Added ErrorCodeUtil to resolve Errors/Identifiers to error codes
Added Singleton for static init of singleton utils
Fixed issue where no existing users lead to an error
Added route guarding and jwt verification as well as a permission system
Now compiling to es2017 to fix issues with array methods
Completed route guard functionality; added documentation
Added logging normal errors on resolveErrorOnRoute
